snippet.title: Yaoling: Mythical Journey | Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Yaoling: Mythical Journey is now available on Steam in early access!

Delve into the Land of the Ancients, venture through many beautiful biomes, befriend hundreds of Yaolings, face off powerful demons, and unveil the mystery of the realm!

_______________________________________________________________

Follow us for updates!
